{"tid":1314050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！ 有市民發起 【懸紅緝兇】！","createTime":"2019-07-14T04:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T04:42:37.000Z","uid":123138,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"27208d666ff3bd92426a7ce0b8ca4fd527cbdb4c","tid":1314050,"uid":123138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"依單野無人講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有單咁既野 示威者肯定識得更保護自己身份<br />\n<br />\n有市民發起【懸紅緝兇】，如果能提供7月13日上水暴亂的暴徒資料，能協助警方緝捕暴徒歸案，每一個最終被捕暴徒的資料提供者將獲獎金港幣500元正！<br />\n<br />\n發起者保證爆料者身份絕對保密。<br />\n<br />\n需要暴徒正面清晰照片，如果能提供個人資料更佳，資料將直接轉交警方，不留任何記錄。<br />\n<br />\n爆料熱線：56051550（whatsapp/微信）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=522311151840399&amp;id=518926118845569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D522311151840399%26id%3D518926118845569&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPagmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=83236ace\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=522311151840399&amp;id=518926118845569</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCMDt11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCMDt11.png&h=64b748a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：時聞新聞<br />\n<br />\n全部連登仔都愛國愛黨 竟然無人話打去爆料熱線報料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持警察 支持成立獨立調查委員會 還警察清白！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f35375cb75033c153995ac9c92ee8ab7aa4d021","tid":1314050,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"我去撐動物示威都起碼有1K+飯盒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa86770317b91fa5edd0669a5688e6952713da2","tid":1314050,"uid":61250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"提供曬警犬屋企人嘅資料"},{"pid":"7a05a13e447fee5f698223868490a6e060658bc7","tid":1314050,"uid":117843,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"咁鬼少<br />\n洗乜講<br />\n<br />\n要報串<br />\n唔比錢都會報<br />\n<br />\n本身唔報<br />\n幾多錢都唔會報"},{"pid":"3fdd5a3540a08f72806ed27205244e1181930746","tid":1314050,"uid":271267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"500???笑撚死"},{"pid":"4194da3e77adc887be0365f3da8dc284df66c893","tid":1314050,"uid":34612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"見唔見gigi mak 金毛肥佬"},{"pid":"b8305ad1b61cbcf4dc0cf5f56fbfaa277e9aba49","tid":1314050,"uid":25367,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"我睇live見到劉馬車，有冇手足cap咗圖"},{"pid":"a7f13b6c3bda460407c4f0a5ee48ee23a67ae7a4","tid":1314050,"uid":271267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"到時啲仆街會唔會話有1000個人提供過同樣資料,每人分5毛?"},{"pid":"d95b93814b48bed56c7f14f0d74fde6f6e9cc80e","tid":1314050,"uid":214534,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"入去亂報左個藍絲後生仔<br />\n咁就賺500<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c398a6891a988773db8e305598d1aab452c552f","tid":1314050,"uid":106302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"屌你 快啲報警察家人俾佢地查<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453e2a41c5c28c66af88bc783d8a8b8c6a56198f","tid":1314050,"uid":36702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x